h life, I ask for a chance that’s fair, a chance to equal my stride, a chance to do or dare. If I should win, let it be by the code, with faith and honor held high, if I should lose, let me stand by the road, and cheer as the winners go by. Day by day, get better and better, until I can’t be beat, won’t be beat. Day by day, get better and better, until I can’t be beat won’t be beat. Amen. Marketing 360, proudly supporting entrepreneurs since 2009. Fuel your Brand.\n---\nHusker Prayer (prayer included in video) - goo.gl/nEXGHt\n\n---\n\nWatch Tribute to Entrepreneurs Part I -\n   • Tribute to Entrepreneurs - Part I  \n\n---\n\nMarketing 360® is the #1 Marketing Platform® for Small Business. It has everything you need from design, to marketing, to CRM. Powered by Madwire® - voted one of the Nation's Best Places to Work by Glassdoor in 2016 \u0026 2017! \n\nFollow Us:\n\nMarketing 360® Website: https://www.marketing360.com/\nMadwire® Website: https://www.madwire.com/\nFacebook:   / marketing360  \nInstagram:   / marketing360  \nTwitter:   / marketing360  \nPinterest:   / marketing360  \nSnapchat:   / fuelyourbrand  \nYoutube:    / marketing360  ","commandRuns":[{"startIndex":18,"length":40,"onTap":{"innertubeCommand":{"clickTrackingParams":"CBgQ040EGAYiEwj7yY-h8riUAxWelgoIHVVhBKVIpr3IqqzzuIIhygEEpYkarg==","commandMetadata":{"webCommandMetadata":{"url":"https://www.youtube.com/redirect?event=video_description\u0026redir_token=QUFFLUhqa2gyaXZuRTh3V0wtMEpWa2NmeGpfVmE0ZUhYd3xBQ3Jtc0tsc2lVXzgweklSUVo1V21ONG1BUkN4VklrRTBhOE00Szd5dEZ0UzI3ZkVwazhZekpRZnBPelFUdDl0NHVrS0VUNVhlUVNkTWNDYlpsTFpaT0d2UjZDUjdPU0xOSzhWbzZGWjZyelJYUDVRR1Y2Q2hoYw\u0026q=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.marketing360.com%2F%3Fref%3DYouTubeTributetoEntrepreneursPart2\u0026v=IQTjmsVSHqY","webPageType":"WEB_PAGE_TYPE_UNKNOWN","rootVe":83769}},"urlEndpoint":{"url":"https://www.youtube.com/redirect?event=video_description\u0026redir_token=QUFFLUhqa2gyaXZuRTh3V0wtMEpWa2NmeGpfVmE0ZUhYd3xBQ3Jtc0tsc2lVXzgweklSUVo1V21ONG1BUkN4Vklr